OL,6,GBBC News will launch a revised schedule
OL,7,Gthis March which will leave the service
OL,8,Gwith no planned facility to cover UK
OL,9,Gbreaking news stories.
OL,11,FExisting UK-only programmes on the BBC
OL,12,FNews Channel will come to an end next
OL,13,Fweek. From 6th March, a new joint
OL,14,FUK/international schedule will see UK
OL,15,Fviewers receive programmes including
OL,16,FWorld Business Report.
OL,18,FInternational viewers will see regular
OL,19,Fnews programmes including Live, Impact
OL,20,Fand Global replaced by the new service.
OL,3,CJoint UK/international BBC News service
OL,4,Cfrom March
