PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F352A1679066607
OL,6,FDetails of the changes were exclusively
OL,7,Frevealed on Pres Cafe on Thursday
OL,8,Fevening, the forum operated by the TV
OL,9,FPres group, of which this website is a
OL,10,Fmember.
OL,12,FThe schedule will be temporary to allow
OL,13,Fstaff and resources to be used to
OL,14,Fprepare for the full launch of the
OL,15,Fcombined channel this April. But during
OL,16,Fthis time, the BBC will temporarily
OL,17,Flose the ability to go live to UK
OL,18,Fviewers only, in the event of a
OL,19,FUK-specific breaking news story.
OL,3,CJoint UK/international BBC News service
OL,4,Cfrom March
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/8
