OL,6,FAd breaks on the international version
OL,7,Fof the new channel will be filled with
OL,8,FUK-focussed content for UK viewers.
OL,9,FIt's not known if World News America
OL,10,Fwill appear on the UK version of the
OL,11,Fchannel later in March, when the time
OL,12,Fdifference between the UK and USA
OL,13,Fshrinks by one hour due to the USA
OL,14,Fstarting daylight savings (summer time)
OL,15,Fearlier than in the UK.
OL,3,CJoint UK/international BBC News service
