OL,6,FNormally, this time difference results
OL,7,Fin changes to the evening schedule,
OL,8,Fpushing The Context to start half an
OL,9,Fhour later in the UK. Elsewhere in the
OL,10,Fevenings, the current 'branded'
OL,11,Fschedule will continue on both
OL,12,Fservices, with Outside Source and The
OL,13,FContext continuing as normal.
OL,15,FFrom April, the BBC plans to use Studio
OL,16,FA, its basement studio with a virtual
OL,17,Fbackdrop, to deliver a back-up UK
OL,18,Fbreaking news facility as and when
OL,19,Frequired. This back-up will be in
OL,20,Foperation between 9am and 11pm (UK
OL,21,Ftime).
