OL,6,FAnd it's been confirmed that new
OL,7,Fdigital streams ` first mentioned in
OL,8,FThe Sunday Times last week as being
OL,9,F"under consideration" ` are in fact
OL,10,Fearmarked for launch later this year.
OL,12,FThe Sunday Times reported that these
OL,13,Fstreams would be Red Button channels
OL,14,Foffering viewers in-depth coverage of
OL,15,Fstories specific to the UK. It's still
OL,16,Funclear what form these will take, but
OL,17,Fit's reminiscent of the News
OL,18,FMultiscreens service offered by the BBC
OL,19,Fin the early days of digital TV, but
OL,20,Fdelivered online.
OL,3,CJoint UK/international BBC News service
OL,4,Cfrom March
