OL,6,FThe latest developments follow warnings
OL,7,Fby regulator Ofcom that it expects the
OL,8,FBBC to continue delivering high quality
OL,9,Fnews content for UK audiences. It's
OL,10,Fthreatened to impose conditions on the
OL,11,FBBC if this doesn't happen.
